Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.50,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,不可思議的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.96,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,這根尾巴在表達什麼感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.08,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,結果桃並沒有告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.78,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,姐姐  你終於向SNS的世界進軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.08,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,良很感動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.44,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,SNS是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.88,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(988.571,989.715)}Sugoi Nettono Sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.88,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,是很厲害的網絡世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.58,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,是Social Network Service
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.10,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,有什麼來了  這是什麼
