Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.10,mazoku - paso2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HD7F4B3&\frz13.72\pos(862.857,996.572)}賬號確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.10,mazoku - paso3,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz12.37\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HD8ED99&\pos(1481.143,786.286)}確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,難不成這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.66,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,但是桃她說了不想告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.61,mazoku - kune,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\an7\c&H8C8A8A&\pos(1189.714,374.858)}肌肉  有氧運動  \N修行  貓  烏冬\N  多魔櫻醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.61,mazoku - kune,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\an7\c&H8C8A8A&\pos(753.143,793.143)}魔法少女  從藝第12年  \N魔力被奪復健中 \N 只要物理毆打就能贏得戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.61,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,這絕對是桃
